1
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:24,440
May I help you, traveler?

2
00:00:25,690 --> 00:00:28,450
Something drew you to my shop...

3
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:31,040
something powerful.

4
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:36,240
Ah, you have a keen eye.

5
00:00:36,390 --> 00:00:39,490
The Alicorn Amulet
is one of the most mysterious

6
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:43,340
and powerful
of all the known magical charms.

7
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:48,460
I'm afraid this is...
far too dangerous.

8
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:53,300
Would you like that gift-wrapped?

9
00:01:00,890 --> 00:01:05,890
Season 3 | Episode 5
Magic Duel

10
